{"tid":1199439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"軍事撚有無辦法整張list列出所有賣武器比香港警察既外國軍火商？","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:29.000Z","uid":40216,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2b2927c41c2dbc1729d3c4e98a2f15730f26a1","tid":1199439,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"本身香港係咪處於美國/歐盟對支那出口禁令範圍内一向都係有模糊地方<br />\n外國政府雖然話唔想直接介入香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但逃犯條例通過之後香港既執法單位等於變成左支那國家機器既一部分<br />\n所以其實係可以比壓力美國/歐盟，要求<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴格執行對支那既軍備出口管制</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">停止向香港警察供應軍火並且唔再容許例如SDU呢d單位同歐美軍警一齊訓練</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而歐盟國家係點樣執行對支那既軍火出口基本上只係得一紙聲明但無統一立場，<br />\n部分國家好似法國同意大利係好寬鬆<br />\n而德國呢d就會係軍火出口既時候考慮埋會否涉及人權問題同係咪符合歐盟整體既利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國就更加唔使講，而且國會兩黨加埋侵宜家係限制對支出口高科技產品既問題上槍口一致<br />\n上年Heckler &amp; Koch已經停止左向警察供貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果要外國施壓，呢個係其中一個可行辦法<br />\n黑警咁想做公安我地咪成全佢地咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於何謂武器既定義可以參考美國US Munitions List，當中包括致命同非致命性既武器: <a href=\"https://www.law.cornell.edu/cfr/text/22/121.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.law.cornell.edu%2Fcfr%2Ftext%2F22%2F121.1&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=ce0bfa8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.law.cornell.edu/cfr/text/22/121.1</a><br />\nEuropean Council 1989年既聲明：<a href=\"https://www.sipri.org/sites/default/files/2016-03/Council-Statement.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sipri.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2016-03%2FCouncil-Statement.pdf&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=d51e9523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sipri.org/sites/default/files/2016-03/Council-Statement.pdf</a><br />\n英國對歐盟聲明既詮釋：<a href=\"https://www.sipri.org/sites/default/files/2016-03/UK-interpretation-of-the-arms-embargo-against-China.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sipri.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2016-03%2FUK-interpretation-of-the-arms-embargo-against-China.pdf&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=a03793da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sipri.org/sites/default/files/2016-03/UK-interpretation-of-the-arms-embargo-against-China.pdf</a><br />\n當中包括<span style=\"color: red;\">any equipment which is likely to be used for internal repression</span><br />\n<br />\n2003-2016年德國向香港出口既武器種類<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.waffenexporte.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Waffen-Ex_Hongkong.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.waffenexporte.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FWaffen-Ex_Hongkong.pdf&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=588d31bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.waffenexporte.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Waffen-Ex_Hongkong.pdf</a><br />\n基本上以手槍，衝鋒槍同自動步槍爲主，買家估下係邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國政府軍火出口原則既第3同第3條總則講到，係德國會否批准軍備出口會考慮接收國有無侵犯人權既記錄，當中會考慮人權組織同歐盟既報告：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.waffenexporte.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/PolitischeGrunds%C3%A4tze_BR_R%C3%BCstung.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.waffenexporte.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F06%2FPolitischeGrunds%25C3%25A4tze_BR_R%25C3%25BCstung.pdf&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=58f434e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.waffenexporte.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/PolitischeGrunds%C3%A4tze_BR_R%C3%BCstung.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"1cf12b833227cf23d67ffed28d893805e3b9632c","tid":1199439,"uid":231040,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"剩係知道德國已經唔俾出口軍火同配件嚟香港，所以嚟緊警犬啲MP5冇零件嘅話就要再搵Source，但而家瑞士同奧地利仲未禁，近年警犬CID同反恐特勤啲槍就係同佢地買...."},{"pid